      <title>《致B-612星球的Zek》</title>
      <link href="/iloveuangel.github.lo/post/6b6573b7.html"/>
      <url>/iloveuangel.github.lo/post/6b6573b7.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\iloveuangel.github.lo\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\iloveuangel.github.lo\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\iloveuangel.github.lo\js\Meting.min.js"></script><center>我曾见过银河<center><center>现独爱你这颗星星<center><center>不知道宇宙是否有尽头<center><center>有你在地方就是我的港口  <center> <br><center>我的小王子<center><center>让我做你的玫瑰<center><center>相守在只有我俩的星球<center><center>不惧任何流言蜚语世俗纷扰<center>   <br><center>你有太阳的热炽<center><center>也似月光般温柔<center><center>尽管不信世上有天长地久<center><center>但此刻只想与你一起白头 <center> <br><center>孤独本是常态<center><center>人生知己难求<center><center>若无人能懂你的忧愁<center><center>请记得永远有我在你背后<center>]]></content>
      
      
